The model for multiple subjects is given by @eq-nlm and the LS estimate is given by

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{split}
\widehat{\psib}
=
\arg\min_{\psib}
\sum_{i=1}^{m}
\sum_{j=1}^{n}
\left(
y_{ij}
-
f(\psib, t_j)
\right)^2
\end{split}
\end{equation}
$$ {#eq-nlm-ls}

```{r}
